Legend:
  W = Work in progress
  D = Done
  P = Postponed
  ? = Questionable

Plans for 0.3.3
===============

    Improvements:
      [D] Preview current data instead of saved file
      [D] Allow selecting arbitrary video file
            [?] Menu item activation
      [D] New toolbar for video
      [D] New window for video player output

    Bug Fixes:
      [D] File marked unchanged after saving a copy of it
      [W] Overwrite dialog not always presented when saving
            * Self typed filename without extension!
      [ ] Open button on the main toolbar missing tooltip

    Other:
      [?] Never use plural names in directory and file names

    Run PyChecker!


Plans for 0.4.0
===============

  New Features:
    [ ] Timing shift
          * Shift amount: seconds/frames
              * Spin buttons
          * Target: selection/all
    [ ] Retiming
          * 2 points, for which current and desired as times/frames
              * Frame: spin button
              * Time: need a new widget, TimeEntry based on CellRendererTime
          * Target: selection/all
    [ ] Fix durations
          * Analysis?
          * Duration per character
          * Minimum time between subs
          * Minimum duration
          * Maximum duration
          * Allow reduce (yes/no)
          * Allow expand (yes/no)
          * No frame units for this one
    [ ] Framerate conversion
          * Input framerate, output framerate
              - Combo boxes
          * Target: selection/all?


Plans after 0.4.0
=================

  New Features:
    [ ] Find, find and replace
          [ ] Regular expressions
                * Support all Python regular expression flags
          [ ] Simple string search
                * Match case
                * Match entire word only
          [ ] Target
                * Selection / current project / all open projects
                * Main text, translation text


Unscheduled
