  * Documentation (HTML)

  * Support for additional subtitle formats

      - Add support for headers
          o Header editing?
          o Header conversion?

      - MPlayerSub/MPSub
        http://www.mplayerhq.hu/DOCS/tech/mpsub.sub

      - SubViewer & SubViewer 2.0

